snippet.title: 【Steel Runner】VR Block Vehicle Craft SandBox  Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
URL：
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2855870/Steel_Runner__VR_Block_Craft_Sandbox

Steel Runner is a VR vehicle crafting sandbox game using physics.
Create your own unique Runner(vehicle) by combining various types of blocks, then ride it to enjoy free exploration, adventure, and combat in an open-world environment!

Please subscribe to our channel and give us a high rating!
